name: VR Seduction
description:
This is a genesis to creating art in virtual reality with Tiltbrush or Openbrush both tools are spectacular and lead us to unsuspected creative paths.
I am happy to take this first step accompanied by the music of another great and talented crypto artist and music producer as ISMO that inspires me to continue on this path that breaks with everything I've been doing.
We both chose a quantum leap to virtual reality in this initial collaboration.
